                        &lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@melpomene I see now.  yes &lt;code&gt;for(size_t i = 0; i &amp;lt; Name[i]; i++ )&lt;/code&gt; should have been &lt;code&gt;for(size_t i = 0; Name[i]; i++ )&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

